ue="Confined Space Permit" />
<p align="center">&nbsp;<span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;"><strong>BYU-Idaho Confined Space Work Permit</strong></span></p>
<table border="0" style="width: 760px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" height="37" width="750">
<h4><span style="color: #000000;">The completed permit must be posted at the work site.</span></h4>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td height="37" width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Permit submitted by</span></strong><span style="font-size: x-small;"> </span></td>
<td height="37" width="532"><input name="Name of person who issued permit" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td height="37" width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Email Address:</span></strong></td>
<td height="37" width="532"><input name="txtEmailFrom" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Date work to be done</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input maxlength="100" name="Date being done" size="55" type="text" />
<p><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small;"><strong>Permit good for 24 hours only!</strong></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Time work to be started</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input maxlength="100" name="Time started" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Time work completed</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input maxlength="100" name="Time completed" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Work Order Number</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input maxlength="100" name="Work Order Number" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Location of work</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input maxlength="100" name="Location of Work" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Nature of work</span></strong><span style="font-size: x-small;"> </span></td>
<td width="532"><input maxlength="100" name="Nature of Work" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Other Hazardous Work</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-small;"><select name="Other Hazardous Work" size="1" style="width: 275; height: 21; font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold;">
<option selected="selected" value="None">None</option>
<option value="Hot Work">Hot Work</option>
<option value="Lockout/Tagout">Lockout/Tagout</option>
<option value="Hazardous Materials">Hazardous Materials</option>
</select></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Entrant/s</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="Entrant/s" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Attendant/s</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="Attendant/s" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">Department or Shop</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="Department/Shop" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;">Oxygen Reading</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="Oxygen Reading" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;">LEL Flammability Reading</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="LEL Flammability Reading" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;">Hydrogen Sulfide Reading</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="Hydrogen Sulfide Reading" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;">Carbon Monoxide Reading</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="Carbon Monoxide Reading" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="218"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;"><strong>Chlorine</strong></span><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-small;"> Reading</span></strong></td>
<td width="532"><input name="Chlorine Reading" size="55" type="text" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<table border="0" style="width: 760px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td height="2"><strong><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Required Check List</span></strong></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<table border="0" style="width: 760px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Hazard Assessment" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Hazard Assessment" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">1. Was a pre-entry hazard assessment conducted?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Lockout/Tagout Required" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Lockout/Tagout Required" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">2. Is Lockout/Tagout required?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Ventilation" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Ventilation" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">3. Is mechanical ventilation required?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Respiratory Protection" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Respiratory Protection" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">4. Is Respiratory protection required?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Communications Equipment" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Communications Equipment" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">5. Do you have communications on site?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Barriers" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Barriers" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">6. Are barriers erected at vault entrance?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="PPE" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="PPE" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">7. Is adequate personal protective equipment being used?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Copy of Permit at work site" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Copy of Permit at work site" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">8. Will a copy of the permit be posted at the work site?</span></strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="119"><strong> <span style="font-family: Arial;"> <input name="Work site secure" type="radio" value="yes" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> Yes </span> <input name="Work site secure" type="radio" value="no" /><span style="font-size: x-small;"> No</span></span></strong></td>
<td width="631">
<p><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">9. Will vault be secured after completion of work?</span></strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<table border="0" style="width: 760px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Print</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: x-small;"> a copy of this permit using your tool bar print function and keep the copy at the work site.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Then click on the "<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Submit Request</span></strong>" button below after printing a copy of the permit.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-small;">Upon completion, e-mail the safety office noting of completion and any problems that may have been encountered. &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: x-small;">IN CASE OF AN EMERGENCY CALL 911 .&nbsp;&nbsp; DO NOT ENTER THE CONFINED SPACE.&nbsp;&nbsp; WAIT FOR RESCUE PERSONNEL.</span></strong><span style="font-size: x-small;"> </span></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
